ì@bb7d0f0e34b1558ef03af0cef6f28451b39fd8c7f9a29cd2abd40c2b45d91073Ö7Title: This week in Nu #44
Path: This week in Nu #44
Content:
charlespierce, fdncred, and jonathandturner got a new release pipeline working to build the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2048] binaries for each release
jonathandturner landed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2015] ``nu-table``
 and new table drawing algorithms
fdncred added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2010] config for the bat-based text viewing
, fixed bugs with 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2035] linked externals
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2054] wix support
JosephTLyons renamed 
``math average``
 to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2014] ``math avg``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2019] bumped heim
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2031] formatted project markdown
, improved the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2040] ``cal``
 command
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2050] ``random uuid``
, and added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2061] ``random bool``
andrasio improved supporting for 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2016] ``math median``
siedentop added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2017] ``--count``
 to 
``uniq``
HiranmayaGundu added tests for 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2022] Windows drive letters
bailey-layzer added errors for 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2030] division by zero
arashout added tests for the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2037] new math functionality
amousa11 added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2043] ``math mode``
zombie110year translated more book chapters to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/book/pull/108] Simplified Chinese
